Semantic Search	Find similar documents or answers based on meaning, not keywords.
Text Classification	Classify emails, reviews, or messages using vector features.
Clustering	Group similar texts together (e.g., topic modeling).
Translation & Summarization	Encode meaning before transforming it.
Chatbots & LLMs	Use embeddings to understand context and retrieve relevant responses.
